Learning Electronics Videos: 1-3 MP4

UcanDo video set on basic (extreme very beginning) electronics, but carries through to semiconductors, transistors, FETs, SCRs - ends on integrated circuits.

If you can get over the 8-bit game graphics used in this video set, there's tremendous fundamental electronics knowledge here! If you own a soldering iron, you should see this.
